<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">


<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Internship Completion Certificate - <%- internship.studentName %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/latter.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>

    <div class="page">
        <!-- Watermark -->
        <div class="watermark">
            <img src="/logo.png" alt="Watermark">
        </div>

        <!-- Header -->
        <header>
            <div class="logo-section">
                <img src="/logo.png" alt="Creative Web Infotech" class="company-logo">
            </div>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> info@cdmi.in</p>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>+91 <%- internship.facultyContactNo.slice(0, 5) + ' ' +
                        internship.facultyContactNo.slice(5) %></p>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-building"></i> UDYAM-GJ-22-0548946</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="yellow-divider"></div>

        <h2 class="document-title">Internship Completion Certificate</h2>

        <div class="date-section">
            <p><strong>Date : <%= new Date().getDate().toString().padStart(2, '0' ) %>-<%= (new Date().getMonth() +
                            1).toString().padStart(2, '0' ) %>-<%= new Date().getFullYear() %></strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="recipient-details">
            <p><strong>To,</strong></p>
            <p><strong><%- internship.studentName %></strong></p>
            <p><%- internship.collegeName %></p>
            <p><strong>Address :</strong>
                <% let addr=internship.address; if (addr.length> 30) {
                    let splitIndex = addr.lastIndexOf(' ', 30);
                    if (splitIndex === -1) splitIndex = 30;
                    let firstLine = addr.substring(0, splitIndex);
                    let secondLine = addr.substring(splitIndex).trim();
                    %>
                    <%- firstLine %><br><%- secondLine %>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <%- addr %>
                                    <% } %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Mob no :</strong>+91 <%- internship.studentContactNo.slice(0, 5) + ' ' +
                    internship.studentContactNo.slice(5) %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="letter-body">
            <p><strong>Dear <%- internship.studentName %>,</strong></p>
            <p>This is to certify that <strong><%- internship.studentName %></strong>, a student of <strong><%-
                        internship.collegeName %></strong>, has successfully completed an internship as a
                <strong><%- internship.internshipPosition %></strong> at <strong>Creative Web Infotech</strong> from
                <strong>
                    <%= internship.startDate ? internship.startDate.split('-').reverse().join('-') : 'N/A' %>
                </strong> to
                <strong>
                    <%= internship.endingDate ? internship.endingDate.split('-').reverse().join('-') : 'N/A' %>
                </strong>.
            </p>
            <p>During the internship, the intern demonstrated excellent skills, professional behavior, and a strong work
                ethic. We wish <%- internship.studentName %> all the best in their future endeavors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="internship-details">
            <p><strong>Details of the Internship:</strong></p>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Internship Position</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%- internship.internshipPosition %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Duration</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%- internship.duration %> Hours</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Starting Date</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= internship.startDate.split('-').reverse().join('-') %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Ending Date</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%= internship.endingDate ? internship.endingDate.split('-').reverse().join('-') : 'N/A' %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Working Time</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%- internship.workingTime %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Mentor</strong></td>
                    <td>: <%- internship.internFacultyName %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>



        <footer>
            <div class="signatures" style="margin-top: 50px;">
                <div class="sign-box">
                    <div class="line"></div>
                    <p><strong>Intern Sign</strong></p>
                </div>
                <div class="sign-box">
                    <div class="line"></div>
                    <p><strong>Creative Web Infotech</strong></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-line"></div>
            <p>401, 4th Floor, City Center Complex, Nr. Yogichowk, Varachha,</p>
            <p>Surat,Gujarat INDIA - 395006 | https://www.cdmi.in/</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>

</html>